{"tid":1383422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<求助>本人是開小食店，想派飯券給子女","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:55:10.000Z","uid":15390,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"13a27ba5dfabfda65355101fd18d08941419d0cb","tid":1383422,"uid":15390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"大家好，<br />\n<br />\n小弟介紹下自己先，我是開小食店的，<br />\n平時也會接仔女放學的。<br />\n看到原來最近很多子女原來生活也開始成問題，<br />\n食個包就去返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，不是很大生意，所以錢就無乜。<br />\n但係野食鋪頭就有大量。所以想支持下大家返學。<br />\n食飽有營養先至有力氣返學嫁嗎<br />\n唔介意嘅話可以過嚟食，<br />\n不過我鋪頭有啲遠，在葵涌<br />\n<br />\n想請問各位冷氣軍師/ 發夢既仔女，我應該怎樣幫助在學仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾啲意見細佬我呀<br />\n邊種方法會好d<br />\n1) 直接發夢去前線派飯卷現金卷？<br />\n(會不會有啲路過既中產貪藍絲小便宜，驚俾人濫用，幫唔到仔女)<br />\n2) 喺Facebook直接出post？<br />\n(但係又驚有狗同埋大量藍絲攻擊，又怕俾人話我博出位）<br />\n3) 將啲飯券就咁喺PP掉落街等人汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n4) 好似撤溪錢咁掉晒去狗狗到，遠距離攻擊？"},{"pid":"bb8c4130874d82eb17b1c756ab39d417482b9aa7","tid":1383422,"uid":238138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"派比人車過去？"},{"pid":"9203a239f09ddefcb875b70dd4237407938b2514","tid":1383422,"uid":89843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"多謝有愛巴打！幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5695457db0e84d1cd423e7ee9fb117a746708fc","tid":1383422,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"睇學生證？"},{"pid":"0eb56fbf4dd1086ce817318bfed657cfc9455d5b","tid":1383422,"uid":123774,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837379f7338422bd58a75d9fec6190f5b2719cc9","tid":